name: Banquet
description:
Day-in and day-out Eloise Honeyfield enjoys the pompous lifestyle of the rich and famous in the early 19th century. But against all of society's  expectation she does not plan to sell herself to the institution of marriage.

Please mind that this is a work in progress!  Feel free to follow me on Instagram.

This is the result of a one-week game jam in Uni.
